{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"show"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"show","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"YES to show alerts in foreground, NO to suppress them (default)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, iOS does not display notification banners when the app is in the foreground."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Enable this to show system notification alerts even when the app is active."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Example","anchor":"Example","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Configure based on app type:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class NotificationConfigManager {","","    func configureForAppType(_ appType: AppType) {","        switch appType {","        case .messaging:","            \/\/ Messaging apps typically handle notifications in-app","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(false)","","        case .ecommerce, .news:","            \/\/ E-commerce and news apps benefit from showing all notifications","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(true)","","        case .game:","            \/\/ Games might want to suppress during gameplay","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(false)","        }","    }","","    func temporarilyDisableForegroundAlerts(during action: () -> Void) {","        let wasEnabled = Pushwoosh.configure.getShowPushnotificationAlert()","        Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(false)","","        action()","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(wasEnabled)","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"UNUserNotificationCenterDelegate","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and use ","type":"text"},{"code":"Pushwoosh.ForegroundPush","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"sections":[],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","title":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setShowPushnotificationAlert:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets whether to show alert for push notifications when app is in foreground."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setShowPushnotificationAlert:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setshowpushnotificationalert:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.P